_UH41gYB7YIr_dp5ynPNyXu0I-dNrs/7" target="_blank"&gt;他退缩了&lt;/a&gt;。巧合的是，在他吹捧的“倒数”税款生效的几个小时后，他这样做了，中国通过将其对美国商品的关税提高到84％而进行了报复。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/wLb01icibskkQuCqRBEsL9UBSy0DD7GXmIk5SongM0C9ZV1-vw1DUk6WfXKncG9lQei0V0g6c9H_j6QW0kTnjfr2slnsYDriWmwkzFWMvRAsAQoGGJkvZfnUGx3axP-rgSCz31d-cvGpdHv3RH7NZJDtKDSpyrtswQvHA4q6HM0Uxn8AdpwORvN1Y6cj2NXJ9exSjO8yJaJg5F0RBR0bTXwGF-fxjLIExE1H0D680zB-7vJ4jFcXhazZMIiSKhYdPlwzmdE3WZBug-PDTAIFd7kV9zJaNp365Fp01KKxy59pgJ8Mj-t6nIteKGB_sKhbx30pD3d8yqA4BXVSOx-r2X2o9TMGIEcxxImU-ZEtpcgGV-M-eqKj1rtY3g/q5oOFlFB1Xc29ryJJ2yXa9fQhs_5LlK4/7" target="_blank"&gt;但是，在呼吁自己的贸易战升级为90天的延迟时&lt;/a&gt;，这是一系列类似的务虚会中的最新和最大的延误，特朗普在来到中国时并没有走开。确实，美国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/yR57z1quNcq5lthqm_0qv2yzdOZEJbffwYXuh1-FN7nNu2mKl2s2sNcrBK6v9a3XadtHcHeQmdXNOKwYGzYxneLubSe6hlA5Qj-Q4-SJxVU7sEJ2-RhMOLz2m_-G0D52IGoGQVL4hofaTpgggCFv1v8KDGD8mqMOvR9hL6Xuz6f_qc6PPWmmFFkDJ03j-7HAFJIrJNdkBfHv-pLDI8Zzi0zbaR2YREof9hoGJCL120JFuBtqCyJdJagS_Z53pWJzLE9EmGdze6KGPGzqJ6gzd3_iYqZEDXI3brtfG2r-qr9TTOkNqgJHDTUxYb9yD7D9xLWY6HCMnOR4N0sgmQTrkEehXoX_maBZ3I05YKgAgAkkJQzqMF8oIpFJIg/5xazUrdNK5IhPLPR4lk3rwIDegVrQbnS/7" target="_blank"&gt;现在将中国商品征税提高到125％&lt;/a&gt; 。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/d3fEJqV-Sci9aykeTVhC6D1IG8ObA1fVstg2t1uHbGJKIHNWFvf2sHilwwNOQN2WJMs9ersG7gv80ExFwC3Czdx4dVUZ1LpOgAf15t5eDh1ntDMtEB2XFb_yBjfIrRqIFbvogfsKCkbyHfdYcZsbn5ChKzcbiDiNblz1xZMUi6TTVcHMw4gYzG2XeLr3xgnZ9neH_RD7XOIXcml3Qp6ltaeG_5XoD3udtEgHVDpGiYSGJQC1Z2T7dWEwJ39SBN5EcllLsnP2AphLCbEkgY7_PFTay3En0apHpn6pZhKweb3IJzA6gi-hHC6c8zsZEpqoYKcmIONXApV2V4Y0I8GvM_igf4wo_u8WL9bGYXEhow-8XvynIaSIVoiS6A/_8ZHC_AW8VEGMCTWwoUTn-lLm9plK-wC/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ikjLrgdq29sI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ikjLrgdq29sI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;截至目前，美国对钢铁，铝和汽车的关税仍处于目前的速度。除了北美贸易协定所涵盖的物品外，加拿大和墨西哥商品的关税对加拿大和墨西哥商品的关税也将保持不变。即使&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/WgTLp9Brh5DHcff-LAsQqM4rduCQsFBdXb1tlwrUgtiLKllV6QYNmLE4uSZyKNWPAyK85rpoSefPRH-HSUFjLzUye0CG_a1KoajNBSLHCUmry2AyJ669vlomoec_XUak-8y37K4wduN9qRYNe8LCIvOGmVGoybH90nw5YA7YuS-zLu7MwwTyHYsnvJQCxiR5T3lWF2TOXRe8I78dz4tCnkQLa92WOU2mKcDqKunXc3DT5WMZGw8IDCjJbFhExgAeskKlrbKbSFct6d3QEooavEDhkPVCUUJfMiUTsVMGyD10pgpVYt9CDw7JxIfxbhl6YQrI0qHO7VKc1XpQZ9t7tbksAVP4qTUYOToMyZObAdoSyG0iurHiHu_oZgk/zWCFwpRqEgbf64sGYOsiHknuhqmw9bMe/7" target="_blank"&gt;集团宣布对金属关税进行报复&lt;/a&gt;，欧洲联盟即使税率仅面临10％的税。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;当特朗普的副官周三下午散发出突然的逆转时，独立的观察者将政府的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7fVw6q7L9EoF_N0jYC6EWW7Umu-7mIB9rGOpXR1iUOneVHeMquXxvm5bNBdOp4Ec0KFfEMdNr-rTLppfEgarcqr_OKtznDmxJQOzVp0J2lX_xSTIa2rQ0PUZO7oWY5D2Bafi_oBj1FeB1yr6MpZ2O1HBQq3xbaqSWRyBlMJeZUHIiKa5tH9Xw2Y3kDzUGIfiO3jg4fjcbKSfbXCN5xqTA48q13BPjN0hIFwgdsV45_aJGyqeZ1gB7x-STuRgB368dym1vXhkOEtxsPj2mFrh4rDlngK4JynrQcPxdcBOPiqTqgAUh4rDLdlcUnRtSiDJy_UVk-lz7xBpU9zr3NfEhHf6Ph7VToAQpAkIFdYCzSuRI3vJwydURIvoj6U/EPA5tdsCQUiWUate_imE-xpJirM_MVOf/7" target="_blank"&gt;部分投降&lt;/a&gt;归因于各个方面的巨大压力以及对市场造成的巨大损害。白宫的转盘还包括针对某些美国公司的关税例外的试用气球和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ZXKQyjXwy-fyn-HogzRGB_xmR15rxVRm0wUvT6gA0xp1TLBSKPftFnGhr1ABCDsg5yNW5z1KZMSrX4C-V7V52Si23fDn01HhxWrwyXvOx2OI52IIMBFFEXnvVUnR51WbUlFurbzLgF1j4wqSffqtqibyzROeb4KGejgrFr9lgINeB9NsjaVv34aYo6sPzSvwaHWnkQWFc60Yuhv8Ci1mNl8iPeK