target="_blank"&gt;优先考虑火星的任务&lt;/a&gt;，并可能与专注于返回月球的立法者发生冲突。问题可能会集中在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/YhHch_cNItZagXc2l9ENLTt_2PJ5hjzN26NbbdRctKTzL1QQl_PZsbH0Y-lZvz0sAo7zDLJ9NPJuiugAGnys-dyztcG8CjGLFFTY-9W05rU5Uu5nHy5r0ZX5UHnWj9ElID4jGwnCi4uJ3R38O9ojqPtPeeTCi32Z1IF06ObfbWHpXsAYoWUcAeIxU-ViuxLnZtCgu7uHuz7D6Fyoj-a9Fu-zxfjra3ADxyqYcwqcYfI_JkV21Sq76pRIBiaoQP17pn5dp530AJUP6N9mqCbK2vvND9yHaKuWltF7WPm2KsbBApLa1mXdmls-lJ6Gz7ymGCh69YV13G8dvIG-CnErZR_goGT4JP8XrkX1w0YnLpfwSfjyKotPC1mnb5w/_WiPk6c-9EIPGhBy0PW9XAa3GqbHbzhD/7" target="_blank"&gt;他与SpaceX和非常规背景的紧密联系&lt;/a&gt;上。在大厅里，举报人将告诉国会通过与中国的联系&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/0cRJg69B55JXocTvdbXttnQyMe31i-W8GfJZfThKShkUeb22LW5suS8_L1Sw6hE32hxU_fsdnwxhM8Ev-uDmMPObUmceUhCBRPVQ5p8WW5OuSoHfQfyv69ntNNsU2wvJU91Cz4trI-a3bi-bA0hLgDVs16I1KUCMBFU8iyZxn3LMjpBdu3erE0w01HzIH4gP9WcR5KE5a-zs54rOkNZQqxbwZAYSQPfk2m0tANN1l1TKkqSRMDczAvbPkxJjCHBd6kZ65AGJfvOPC8KdBd3pvJJtwNuyAOsknTTFzYTSnYggiYn8FmVntsx2hY7VtLkKDGGoBb9fmln-6j4jE4NeFJW0EABOhyCMrf6hbTLlJyjnWb7h0WuY6icO480/VUOnfexnU9t6JXiLjDppupGsSenE11fK/7" target="_blank"&gt;威胁到美国的利益&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/sLsvhl7gR78I6hdDCCz-ZtMv5qhbGgJxx4xOotJYztbG-Aj5ic7I6rrPYhz0boTHUq80Upg1YL7O8jvEjJuM-ld1EzO_E0-F189sQ5fHuUOZV4_o1J0BdjgCB-N3rLr9z2rFmxqcu1EDwtacNgUX8yV3joIAww7cHIoArAX6COT63vx8qdtyti22cFxD-HkK0k8nPpGvPRiSZz90sT99KvN5mKFJ0w5YcQqvnoxCV94hKfYsL-nngPavlwzMLFpRSdx8N4Fmgl5zME7bTldvCB6McQM_5XIrEV1LmdpiMQu1s7SdR2QrYmUdc6LTU-aiUFiyblfTx2QUfcthj1mvbdVM6xm3sWO_g2kXbc0UV8bD0P5yeN1nflhX3qtsC4eHMq8FXdiklA5twXYaFmvVzBT13igeSn6nWeEBDSgzaOzzI8J9EGEVxUk-OIRkHAt-Yc0oNJWcNHwU_yvfJVX6c-c4KJkEHdDaZckh7lS_LC-kjsS1L7Bl3KXrM-qmwoJr8irGtxoP2k8J9ucH4KsmiPQ